OOC: The trees climb to a hundred feet into the air with a fairly
dense canopy, it would not be possible to see Tuscon from where they
were unless he were to fly quite high. And then once the group enters
the jungle even that wont be possible unless they are in a clearing
and Tuscon is almost right over them.

&lt;Back In Character&gt;

POLAR CLAW nodded as he stepped out of the shuttle and looked at
NIGHTSHIFT strangely, &quot;I saw something before we landed. That is the
direction that we are headed.

After a moment PROWL came out of the shuttle as well as RAMULUS and
WOLFGANG each of them being handed a small pack by PROWL.

POLAR CLAW threw a small pack at NIGHTSHIFT, expecting him to catch
it. &quot;Its energon rations.&quot; He said by way of explaination. &quot;I don&#39;t
recall seeing any refueling stations in there.&quot;

Around them the trees were rising up to nearly one hundred feet into
the air with a dense canopy of leaves and limbs. The sounds of animals
and birds could be heard coming from within the jungle.

Looking at the uneven and even treacherous terrain once they got
further into the jungle POLAR CLAW looked back at NIGHTSHIFT, &quot;You
don&#39;t look like you will do well in here, you sure you want to come
with us?&quot;

Sure enough there was a path leading in, and at the moment it was flat
enough, but all too soon in the distance one could easily see the path
getting more and more dangerous with tree roots and other natural
obstacles getting in the way.

